headline: Rollins Receives Inaugural Investment Grade Credit Ratings From Fitch and S&P
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) ("Rollins" or the "Company"), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, today announced that Fitch Ratings ("Fitch") and S&P Global Ratings ("S&P") have issued inaugural investment grade credit ratings for the Company.
